title: Cannot automatically insert username and password for Weight Watchers
content: At any time after startup, cannot use log in and password insertion feature. Login and Password retained in Firefox. All other sites responsive.
creator: tedulinski

title: Disable mail notification on Windows
content:
I disable Desktop notifications on Gmail and do not allow any notification in firefox preference. But gmail notifications keep showing up with an annoying sound whenever I use firefox. Please help me to disable it. Thank you.

p/s: I don't install any plugins.
creator: dannydyvn

title: Firefox Hanging on AMD laptop
content:
Every once in a while it hangs and have to force shut down the computer it happens on watching videos or regular websites it hangs in a way that cant move the mouse or see any activity from the HDD led or do anything it s just frozen in there.

my laptop is HP 14 DK1003DX AMD Silver 3050U with Radeon graphics 4 gb ram and 480 ssd WD M.2
